targets.rawSql:
SELECT wsi as label, COUNT(wsi) as value
FROM systems
GROUP BY wsi LIMIT 50

SELECT wsi as label, COUNT(wsi) as value
FROM systems
GROUP BY wsi
ORDER BY count(*)
SELECT latitude, longitude, wsi, geom FROM systems LIMIT 50
SELECT latitude, longitude, wsi, geom, image_url FROM systems LIMIT 50
SELECT COUNT(wsi), wsi FROM systems GROUP BY wsi LIMIT 50
SELECT id, point_id, name, latitude, longitude, wsi, country FROM systems LIMIT 50

SELECT 'Point' as app, 'Communities' as target_app, count(c.point_id) as req_rate
from points p
join communities c on p.id = c.point_id
WHERE p.id = '01H0B2F5R8MM36EQBJAS7MAHHM'
group by p.id, c.point_id
union all
SELECT 'Point' as app, 'Systems' as target_app, count(s.point_id) as req_rate
from points p
join systems s on p.id = s.point_id
WHERE p.id = '01H0B2F5R8MM36EQBJAS7MAHHM'
group by p.id, s.point_id
union all
SELECT 'Communities' as app, c.name as target_app, count(c.point_id) as req_rate
from points p
join communities c on p.id = c.point_id
WHERE p.id = '01H0B2F5R8MM36EQBJAS7MAHHM'
group by p.id, c.name
union all
SELECT 'Systems' as app, s.name as target_app, count(s.point_id) as req_rate
from points p
join systems s on p.id = s.point_id
WHERE p.id = '01H0B2F5R8MM36EQBJAS7MAHHM'
group by p.id, s.name
